text: Arcade was incredibly affordable! While I did not personally partake in the buffet a few family members did enjoy it for the most part. Their deal with the buffet and game card combined is a great value. One of my family members was lucky enough to win a  Nintendo Switch as well!

name: Douglas Baldwin
text: Kids love it. It is like Chuckee Cheese and a decent establishment had a baby. The games are of decent quality, and there is even a movie theatre-like section where you can eat your pizza buffet. The desserts were especially good. Pizza was â€¦More

text: Great time here. We went on a Thursday evening so it wasn't a big crowd. Playtime was great. All the games worked. (Nonworking games are a big pet peeve for me) Staff looked young so teenagers for the most part but they were very helpful â€¦More
